column5: i wish i was maybe 10 years older? being young is not that cool. my only privilege as a kid is that my parents pay for everything and i dont have to work for it. if i was 24 i would have much more permissions. i would be able to go to bed and wake up when i want to, i would be able to drive a car, i would be able to live alone, i would be able to change my name, i would be able to have crush on celebrities and it won't be considered as pedophilia. maybe i even would be less depressed because parents wouldn't control my life.
please, for the sake of.. whatever, go to sleep. you deserve a better person and she's not worth your health.
i am so, so much sorry for you. some part of me died reading this. this is incredibly sad. i wish you well. i really hope you will get better.
i am half of your age but i absolutely feel you. i hope you will get over this. sending love.
